as ECBA compliant / application for authorization;

Review control description: A bank not complying with provisions of section 11 (1) of the Banking Regulation
Act, 1949 (AACS) is required to obtain prior approval of the Reserve Bank for:
(1) Sale of bank's own premises;

Review control description: Delivery process
